TextEng: Back to the grave, you undead beast!
Are you Karlat Jhareg?
Why is this tower so full of fire?
Text: 왜 이 탑은 불로 가득한 거죠?

TextEng: Why do you sound so confused?
Be at peace. I am the Judge you seek.
You be Mister Karlat, yuh?
Why you sound confused?
Yuh, me be da Judge-guy.
Why there so much fire here?
Die, Mister Undead Beast! Die again!
Tell me more...
Get to the point.
Yuh? Ooh, you keep talking...
You got point? Get to it.
Tell me more...
Get to the point.
Yuh? Ooh, you keep talking...
You got point? Get to it.
Will you give that as a written oath?
I've spoken to Quint. He tells a different story.
Text: 퀸트와 얘기했습니다. 그는 다른 이야기를 하던데요.

TextEng: This your journal?
I still have some questions.
You gives that as written oath?
Me talk to Quint already. His story different.
Text: 나 퀸트랑 얘기했어. 그 사람 다른 말했어.

TextEng: Me still have questions.
Why would Quint do such a thing?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> A lich's phylactery, huh? Aren't liches evil?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 리치의 성구함이라고요? 리치는 악한 존재 아닌가요?

TextEng: Who has the phylactery now?
Text: 지금 그 성구함은 누가 가지고 있나요?

TextEng: What about Lathander and the Guardian?
But why Quint do horrible thing like that?
Text: 퀸트 왜 그런 나쁜 짓 했어?

TextEng: Who has philacta-thingy now?
What 'bout da Guardian an' her god?
All right, enough questions.
Okay, 'nuff questions, yuh?
You tricked your brother into the crime.
Text: 당신이 동생을 속여서 범죄에 끌어들인 거군요.

TextEng: You sought undeath out of a greed for knowledge.
Text: 당신은 지식에 대한 탐욕으로 언데드가 되려 했군요.

TextEng: You acted on the advice of someone named Belial.
Text: 당신은 벨리알이라는 자의 조언을 따른 거군요.

TextEng: Nothing. It doesn't say anything of note.
Text: 아무것도 아닙니다. 주목할 만한 내용이 없네요.

TextEng: You tricked Quint into da crime.
Text: 너 퀸트 속여서 나쁜 짓 시켰어.

TextEng: You greedy for knowledge. That's why you undead.
Some guy called Belial, he tell you to do stuff.
Huh? Oh, it not say anything important...
That's all it said. Will you give that as a written oath?
Text: 그게 전부입니다. 그걸 서면 맹세로 해주시겠습니까?

TextEng: Uh, that's all it said. You gives that as written oath?
Text: 어, 그게 전부야. 서면 맹세로 해줘?
